OL,3,CFast-food outlet ordered to pay
OL,4,Cthousands of pounds for illegally
OL,5,Cdumping waste
OL,7,FA fast-food outlet in Buckinghamshire
OL,8,Fhas been ordered to pay thousands of
OL,9,Fpounds after illegally dumping waste
OL,10,Fin a town centre.
OL,12,FCommercial waste from Aylesbury Grill
OL,13,F(operated by Aylesbury Grill House
OL,14,FLtd) was left by street litter bins at
OL,15,FKingsbury, Aylesbury, on several
OL,16,Foccasions in early summer 2023.
OL,18,FThe street litter bins are provided
OL,19,Ffor members of the public to dispose
OL,20,Fof small amounts of personal litter
OL,21,Fonly.
