OL,7,FBuckinghamshire Council said
OL,8,Fbusinesses producing waste are
OL,9,Frequired by law to ensure their waste
OL,10,Fis dealt with properly. It usually
OL,11,Fmeans taking out a trade waste
OL,12,Fcontract.
OL,14,FAylesbury Grill House Ltd was warned
OL,15,Fabout its failings in dealing with its
OL,16,Fbusiness waste by Buckinghamshire
OL,17,FCouncil.
