OL,4,Cthousands of pounds for illegally
OL,5,Cdumping waste
OL,7,FOfficers from the council's Waste
OL,8,FEnforcement Team carried out follow-up
OL,9,Finvestigations in July 2023 using
OL,10,Fevidence found by examining the
OL,11,Fcontents of sacks of waste dumped in
OL,12,Fthe square and town centre CCTV camera
OL,13,Ffootage.
OL,15,FDuring a court case, District Judge
OL,16,FSharma accepted that the actions in
OL,17,Fthis case were deliberate, and that
OL,18,Fthe offending had caused a significant
OL,19,Feyesore and hygiene hazards.
