OL,5,Cdumping waste
OL,7,FAylesbury Grill House Ltd was fined
OL,8,F#6,000 and ordered to pay full clean-
OL,9,Fup and investigation costs to
OL,10,FBuckinghamshire Council, totalling
OL,11,F#3,862.74.
OL,13,FA victim surcharge of #2,400 was also
OL,14,Fimposed meaning that the company has
OL,15,Fto pay a total of #12,262.74 with
OL,16,Fpayment required within 28 days.
