OL,4,Cthousands of pounds for illegally
OL,5,Cdumping waste
OL,7,FThomas Broom, Buckinghamshire
OL,8,FCouncil's Cabinet Member for Climate
OL,9,FChange and Environment said: "We abhor
OL,10,Ffly-tipping in the countryside, but
OL,11,Fthis scandalous dumping of commercial
OL,12,Fwaste in Aylesbury town centre over a
OL,13,Fprotracted period is just as bad.
OL,15,F"Irresponsible disposal of waste from
OL,16,Ffood businesses can promote the spread
OL,17,Fof diseases and Buckinghamshire
OL,18,FCouncil's action here was taken to
OL,19,Fshow that this commercial behaviour
OL,20,Fwill not be tolerated."
