OL,7,FMr Broom added: "Buckinghamshire
OL,8,FCouncil has launched a bold campaign
OL,9,Fin recent weeks against littering,
OL,10,Fcalled, 'For Bucks Sake!'.
OL,12,F"It introduces a higher fixed penalty
OL,13,Fof #500 for the dropping and leaving
OL,14,Fof litter. This court prosecution
OL,15,Fshows that we will not hesitate to act
OL,16,Feven more vigorously in serious cases
OL,17,Fsuch as this."
